For the PRP tests, if enabled, the tool relies on:
- gw_utility.h and gw_utility.c written by Paul Underwood and distributed via
  mersenneforum.org.
- the gwnum library by George Woltmann.


Regarding GMP:
- number sequence definitions may rely on GMP for outputing their value
- it is used for PRP testing (PRP testing is optional an)
